replies.body:
Unfortunately Riot doesn't care about that. The IFS rarely works, and if you screenshot everything, highlight the bad stuff, and send it to them in a ticket, they say "Thanks for reaching out to us. We're not going to do anything. Use IFS".

What is the point in them even having a selection in the drop down menu for a ticket dedicated to reporting such behaviour if they don't care?

{{sticker:sg-lulu}}
